<h1>The heartbeat</h1>
<h2>ERPAL's central activity stream</h2>
<p>
This is an activity stream of ERPAL. The global heartbeat will you show the recent activities of all users. The tab "Own heartbeat" will display only your recent activities. 
You can filter the heartbeat for a specific user, the date and the type of content.
If you are working in a project, a project related activity stream will appear on the project page. This will help you to see the latest activity of your project's team.
</p>